        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/20130737/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/20130737/" class="">第1页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1821514/" class=" " title="季米">季米</a>
                (Life is simple!)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="20130737">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class=""> 近百多年中国历史，近三十年变化最大，但是根子还是没有动。作者广征博引，尤其引用海外学人观点颇多，读来还是可以得到一些启发的。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-08-04 17:24</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
